{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, we consider their findings to be relevant to support Inclusive Teaching even if the concept is not explicit in their text.",
    "In Table 3, we present a summary of the contributions of these works.",
    "From the content and network analysis results, we identified that most literature reviews explored two types of themes: research about gamification itself and its application.",
    "We called these two types \"gamification\" and \"gamification in. \"",
    "Table 4 summarizes the themes explored by gamification literature reviews from 2014 to 2022."
  ]
}